Contract tests for webhooks and billing. You already have a strong test culture. The highest ROI additions are golden payload tests for Merge and Stripe, including replay, reordering, missing fields, and “old timestamp” cases.

Permission regression tests. Build a tiny suite that asserts “user from org A can never read org B resource”, across the routes that touch transcripts, landing pages, and embeddings.

